<section data-bs-version="5.1" class="header11 cid-tB1vWdJbT6" id="header11-a">
   <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center">

         <div class="col-12 col-md">
            <div class="text-wrapper text-center">
               <p class="mbr-text mbr-fonts-style display-7">
                  <strong>Erexafil™</strong> is a daily men's dietary supplement formulated with a carefully selected blend of botanical extracts, adaptogenic herbs, essential vitamins, and minerals commonly used in men's wellness products. It is designed for men who want a convenient once-daily supplement that fits easily into their everyday routine while complementing a healthy lifestyle. Instead of relying on complicated regimens, Erexafil provides a simple approach to nutritional support using ingredients that have long histories of traditional use and ongoing scientific interest.
                  <br><br>

                  The formula includes ingredients such as Horny Goat Weed, Ashwagandha Root Extract, Korean Ginseng, Tribulus Terrestris, Ginkgo Biloba, Muira Puama, Zinc, Vitamin D3, Niacin, and other plant-based compounds. Many of these ingredients have been individually studied for their potential roles in supporting men's health, energy metabolism, and overall wellness. While research exists for several individual ingredients, the complete Erexafil formula itself has not been established as clinically proven to produce specific health outcomes. Manufactured with convenience in mind, Erexafil is intended for adults looking to add a nutritional supplement to their daily wellness routine alongside balanced nutrition, regular physical activity, and healthy lifestyle habits.
               </p>
            </div>
         </div>

         <div class="col-12 col-md-5 image-wrapper">
            <img class="w-100"
                 src="assets/images/erexafil-what-is.webp"
                 alt="Erexafil Men's Daily Wellness Supplement">
         </div>

      </div>
   </div>
</section>




         <!-- How Does Erexafil Work Section -->
<section data-bs-version="5.1" class="header3 cid-tB85bPoWQz" id="erexafil-how-it-works">
   <div class="align-center container">
