            <h4 class="mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-7">
               <br>
               Erexafil™ combines botanical extracts, vitamins, and minerals commonly found in men's wellness supplements. While individual ingredients have been studied for various roles in nutrition and wellness, results vary from person to person, and the supplement should be used alongside a healthy lifestyle.
            </h4>

            <div class="mbr-text mbr-fonts-style display-7">
               <ul>

                  <li>
                     <strong>Supports Men's Daily Wellness</strong><br>
                     Erexafil contains a blend of herbs and essential nutrients selected for men's nutritional support. Its ingredients are commonly included in wellness formulas intended to complement healthy habits and help maintain overall vitality as part of a balanced lifestyle.
                  </li>

                  <li>
                     <strong>Includes Traditional Botanical Ingredients</strong><br>
                     The formula features ingredients such as Horny Goat Weed, Tribulus Terrestris, Korean Ginseng, and Muira Puama, all of which have long histories of traditional use in men's wellness products and continue to be the subject of nutritional research.
                  </li>

                  <li>
                     <strong>Provides Nutritional Support for Energy Metabolism</strong><br>
                     Vitamin D3, Niacin, Zinc, and other nutrients included in Erexafil contribute to normal physiological functions, including energy metabolism. These nutrients are intended to complement a nutritious diet and active lifestyle rather than replace them.
                  </li>

                  <li>
                     <strong>Features Adaptogenic Herbs</strong><br>
                     Adaptogenic ingredients such as Ashwagandha and Korean Ginseng are widely used in dietary supplements. They have traditionally been included in formulations designed to support general wellness and help the body adapt to everyday physical and mental demands.
                  </li>

                  <li>
                     <strong>Contains Ingredients Commonly Used in Circulation & Cognitive Formulas</strong><br>
                     Ginkgo Biloba is a well-known botanical that has been researched for its potential role in supporting healthy circulation and cognitive function. Its inclusion adds to the formula's broad nutritional profile alongside other plant-based ingredients.
                  </li>

                  <li>
                     <strong>Simple Once-Daily Capsule</strong><br>
                     Erexafil is designed as a convenient once-daily dietary supplement, making it easy to incorporate into an existing wellness routine. Consistent daily use, together with healthy lifestyle choices, may help support long-term nutritional goals.
                  </li>

               </ul>

               <p>
                  Erexafil is intended as a dietary supplement to complement healthy eating, regular exercise, quality sleep, and other positive lifestyle habits. It is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.
               </p>

            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</section>





        
