                            <div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer" id="collapse6_28" class="panel-collapse noScroll collapse" role="tabpanel">
                                <div itemprop="text" class="panel-body">
                                    <p class="mbr-fonts-style panel-text display-7">
                                        If you currently take prescription medications, other dietary supplements, or have a diagnosed medical condition, consult your healthcare provider before adding Erexafil to your routine. A healthcare professional can help determine whether the ingredients are appropriate for your individual circumstances.
